25:51.134 --> 25:55.055
It's all my business.
You need to remember that, Lachlan.

25:55.138 --> 25:56.139
Listen, Micah--

25:56.223 --> 25:59.893
You listen.
Don't mistake my kindness for weakness.

25:59.977 --> 26:02.396
One call, I can have you
removed from the board.

26:02.479 --> 26:05.315
I think we're just--
We're all a little raw right now.

26:05.399 --> 26:06.400
Are we?

26:07.651 --> 26:09.903
I can't be here right now. I'm leaving.

26:25.961 --> 26:27.004
Can I help you?

26:29.548 --> 26:32.467
