31:38.106 --> 31:41.818
and just stomping him in his head
and just stomping him.

31:44.404 --> 31:46.949
They threw us in the brig,
beat us both with clubs.

31:47.032 --> 31:49.576
Beat me until I didn't know
my fucking name.

31:50.160 --> 31:52.538
Dishonorable discharge for both of us.

31:54.873 --> 31:57.584
But when I got out,
I never took orders again.

32:00.212 --> 32:01.380
From anybody.

32:02.881 --> 32:05.050
Do you think those boxing matches

32:05.133 --> 32:09.304
and that beatdown led to your
current medical issues?

32:14.643 --> 32:17.771
Yes. I do.

32:23.735 --> 32:26.572
That old junkyard dog won in the end,
didn't he?

32:31.159 --> 32:33.370
He's gonna rob me of everything I love.

32:38.792 --> 32:39.960
Ain't that a bitch?

33:01.773 --> 33:05.611
Ramon Tomas. Inspector Aames.
You mind if we talk?

33:05.694 --> 33:07.571
I'm busy. Fuck off.

33:07.654 --> 33:12.701
Or we can do this down at the station,
of course, but, you know, coffee.

33:19.833 --> 33:20.834
Here you go.

33:24.087 --> 33:27.132
So, give me a reason to believe

33:27.216 --> 33:29.635
Ramon Tomas had nothing to do
with this murder.

33:30.302 --> 33:31.720
Right now, we got you on motive.

33:31.803 --> 33:36.517
You got no alibis,
and... you got a record.

33:36.600 --> 33:37.893
No, I don't.

33:38.810 --> 33:40.354
