35:14.907 --> 35:17.201
At your pain. Your grief.

35:17.284 --> 35:19.161
-Your life's manifestations.
-Does anyone know where he is?

35:19.244 --> 35:21.246
-All she cares about is money. Your money.
-Anyone?

35:21.330 --> 35:23.540
Selling you grade A organic bullshit.

35:23.624 --> 35:25.375
